<lb n="0852a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0889a18" ed="R041"/><cb:juan n="1" fun="close"><cb:jhead>般若波羅蜜多心經斵輪解<note place="inline">終</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
